# Project Structure

This is a Node.js/TypeScript project for parsing and processing nonprofit organization data.

## Key Directories
- `src/`: Main source code directory
  - `scripts/`: Contains various data processing scripts
  - `db/`: Database models and connection logic
  - `crawlee/`: Web crawling functionality
  - `utils/`: Shared utility functions
  - `data/`: Data processing and transformation logic
  - `types.ts`: TypeScript type definitions
  - `index.ts`: Main application entry point

## Important Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json): Project configuration and dependencies
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json): TypeScript configuration
- [src/types.ts](mdc:src/types.ts): Core type definitions
- [src/index.ts](mdc:src/index.ts): Application entry point
